name: Sleep No More
description: Sleep No More is an immersive and interactive theater experience that takes place in the McKittrick Hotel. Audience members can explore various rooms, following actors and experiencing a unique, mysterious storyline.

name: Wicked
description: Wicked is a hugely popular Broadway musical, based on the novel 'Wicked: The Life and Times of the Wicked Witch of the West'. It offers a captivating story and impressive performances that make it a must-see for theater enthusiasts.

name: MET Museum
description: The MET Museum is one of the largest and most prestigious art museums in the world. It houses an extensive collection of art from various cultures and periods, making it a paradise for art lovers.

name: Hex & Co
description: Hex & Co is a popular board game cafe where visitors can enjoy a wide selection of board games while savoring delicious food and drinks. It's a perfect spot for friends and families to have a fun and entertaining time together.

name: Wollman Rink
description: Wollman Rink is an iconic ice-skating rink located in Central Park. During winter, it offers a delightful ice-skating experience with a picturesque view of the park's surroundings.

name: Grace Street
description: Grace Street is a cozy cafe specializing in Korean-inspired desserts and beverages. It offers a wide range of bingsu (shaved ice) and other sweet treats that are perfect for satisfying your dessert cravings.

name: Central Park
description: Central Park is a renowned urban park in Manhattan, New York City. It offers a beautiful landscape, recreational activities, and cultural events, making it a cherished spot for both locals and tourists alike.

name: Brooklyn Botanical
description: The Brooklyn Botanical Garden is a stunning oasis of natural beauty in the heart of Brooklyn. It features a diverse collection of plants and flowers, enchanting visitors with its serene and picturesque settings.

name: High Line
description: The High Line is a unique public park built on an old elevated railway track. It offers a refreshing escape from the city's hustle and bustle with beautifully landscaped gardens, art installations, and scenic views.

name: Columbia University
description: Columbia University is an esteemed Ivy League institution, known for its academic excellence and historic campus. It offers a blend of educational opportunities and cultural diversity in the bustling city of New York.

name: 9/11 Tribute Museum
description: The 9/11 Tribute Museum offers a poignant and educational experience, sharing personal stories and artifacts related to the tragic events of September 11, 2001. It serves as a tribute to the victims, survivors, and heroes of that day.

name: Grand Central
description: Grand Central Terminal is a historic transportation hub in Midtown Manhattan. With its stunning architecture and vibrant atmosphere, it offers more than just a transit point; it's a destination in itself.

name: Thai Market
description: Thai Market offers an authentic and delightful Thai dining experience. With its flavorful dishes, friendly ambiance, and prompt service, it has become a go-to spot for Thai cuisine enthusiasts in Manhattan.

name: The Ellington
description: The Ellington is a charming jazz club that pays homage to the legendary Duke Ellington. With its soulful music, cozy setting, and talented musicians, it's a must-visit destination for jazz lovers in the city.

name: Nan Xiang 小籠包
description: Nan Xiang Xiao Long Bao is a renowned restaurant in Flushing, Queens, famous for its delicious and authentic Shanghai-style soup dumplings. Food enthusiasts from all over the city come to indulge in these flavorful delights.

name: Wuish Kitchen & Bar
description: Wuish Kitchen & Bar offers a contemporary take on traditional Taiwanese cuisine. With its creative dishes, trendy ambiance, and friendly staff, it has become a popular spot for foodies exploring the culinary scene in Brooklyn.

name: Ho Foods
description: Ho Foods is a cozy and inviting eatery specializing in Taiwanese beef noodle soup, a comfort food loved by many. Their dedication to quality ingredients and authentic flavors makes them a favorite among noodle enthusiasts.
